These are Puzzles for 5x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-1::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: snowmobile, ship
2 different games are played: billiard, monopoly
There are 2 different nationalities: nigerian, pakistani
2 different pets are kept: chinchilla, horse
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, coach
1. the pakistani is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
2. the owner of the horse is on the far left##1
3. the person playing billiard is in an even position##4
4. the coach is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Transport   | snowmobile     | ship     |
| Game   | monopoly     | billiard |
| Nationality   | nigerian | pakistani  |
| Pet           | horse    | chinchilla |
| Job         | coach   | designer       |

