.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-2::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: aconite, zinnia
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, subway
There 2 different types of food: garlic, blueberry
2 different pets are kept: dog, lizard
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: surfing, volleyball
1. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
2. the person eating garlic is the person driving the boat##1
3. the person eating garlic is in an even position##4
4. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Flower      | zinnia    | aconite |
| Transport           | subway  | boat     |
| Food   | blueberry       | garlic      |
| Pet           | dog        | lizard      |
| Sport         | volleyball | surfing     |

