.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: puzzles, sudoku
House: colonial, townhouse
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, milk
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: drama, comedy
The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, skateboard
1. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an odd position##4
4. the townhouse house is the person driving the skateboard##1
5. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby         | sudoku     | puzzles    |
| House           | colonial     | townhouse |
| Beverage   | milk    | fanta   |
| Movie-Genre         | drama | comedy   |
| Transport     | helicopter | skateboard |

