.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-4::.
There 2 different types of food: cranberry, kiwi
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, horror
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, dunhill
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, october
City: hamburg, london
1. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
2. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |
| Food          | kiwi     | cranberry     |
| Movie-Genre   | action   | horror        |
| Cigar   | dunhill      | aristoff         |
| Birthday   | october | august       |
| City         | hamburg  | london |

