.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-20::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: rose, azalea
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: country, metal
2 different pets are kept: ferret, hedgehog
The people have 2 different jobs:  dressmaker, engineer
There are 2 different favourite colors: blood-red, ebony
1. the engineer is the fan of country##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far right##1
3. the person who growsazalea is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of country is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| Flower      | azalea      | rose     |
| Music-Genre   | metal    | country  |
| Pet           | ferret   | hedgehog |
| Job         | dressmaker | engineer |
| Color     | blood-red     | ebony     |

 